Overview:

- 'make all' in MDD/MDE creates new tables in $(addpprefix $(FAMILY)/, $(CORES)) under $(TOPDIR)/MDD/.

- 'make all' in MDD/MDF crates the merged tables in $(TOPDIR)/MDD/$(FAMILY)/.

- 'make check' in MDD/MDE and MDD/MDF requires 'make all' in DOC, and check againts the MDS DTD.

-- BD3

